{"tid":1276280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[侵侵教路]一定要有講民主﹑普選訴求既標語同文宣！！","createTime":"2019-07-02T02:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:43:03.000Z","uid":2140,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ff0b82fc1dd1ce4c95071b76a7f91f5b1482672a","tid":1276280,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"&quot;Well, they're looking for democracy and I think most people want democracy. Unfortunately, some governments don't want democracy,&quot; Mr Trump told reporters at the White House.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;That's what it's all about. It's all about democracy. There's nothing better.&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\nEarlier, Mr Trump said the unrest in Hong Kong was &quot;very sad.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n分析：大家都知侵侵講野既Style係最簡單直接，小學雞都聽得明<br />\n我地要勾結外國勢力，一定要用最簡單易入口既message，將件事還原做本質<br />\n你話要林鄭下台，佢地會心諗邊撚個Carrie Lam<br />\n你話暫緩不等於撤回，但係西方政壇黎講暫緩得就係撤回左，佢地唔會明個利害<br />\n<br />\n但係如果話We want democracy 我諗西方社會連小學生都知道係好撚重要既野<br />\n鍵戰都係咁話，如果琴日有義士入到去係舉We want democracy，西媒一定可以大做新聞講香港既政制係點樣點樣不民主<br />\n大家要記住，冇得普選係西方人眼中就好似香港人睇內地既政制一樣咁荒謬<br />\n亦都好簡單將成個香港政權定義為極權政府，人民係為推翻暴政而行動<br />\n一日政制未民主，一日運動都唔會完"},{"pid":"82b13dd4979515285ba50e19f7822d621b534af2","tid":1276280,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"只要係爭取民主普選，我地做乜野都會有光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d455a9425eb4bf2c7ed4f575d58dc98308ecea","tid":1276280,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb32a831bc37cc28263006fe432617d43428c73","tid":1276280,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96b00fd33cf58aa35f5b93e7ddd2b6ca289027a","tid":1276280,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike"